      </paragraph>
      <paragraph>
       Finally, as mentioned earlier, Waaler's [13] proof system coincides with {a mathematical formula}AXn′ in terms of provable sentences [13, Theorem 15]. Thus, Theorem 45 further establishes an exact correspondence to Waaler's axiomatic proposal as well.
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph label="Corollary 47">
